5f8fef2b0819133693deb4c2c2c8837ad12cd05a.sql:
SELECT 
    SUM(ii.`total_amount`) AS total_invoice_amount
FROM 
    `ems-portal-service`.`invoice_info` ii
JOIN 
    `ems-warehouse-service`.`warehouse_info` wi ON ii.`warehouse_id` = wi.`id`
WHERE 
    wi.`city_id` IN (SELECT `id` FROM `ems-portal-service`.`quick_code_master` WHERE `name` = 'Gurgaon') LIMIT 1000

b7b6920733c8c4f59660fc1aa06a05612d444c6d.sql:
SELECT 
    wi.`id`, wi.`warehouse_code`, wi.`warehouse_name`
FROM 
    `ems-warehouse-service`.`warehouse_info` wi
JOIN 
    `ems-portal-service`.`quick_code_master` qcm ON wi.`city_id` = qcm.`id`
WHERE 
    qcm.`name` = 'Gurgaon' LIMIT 1000

521f8e72b2642c8a88fb90d240665e62f5afee99.sql:
SELECT 
    ui.`full_name` AS vendor_name, COUNT(ii.`id`) AS invoice_count
FROM 
    `ems-portal-service`.`invoice_info` ii
JOIN 
    `ems-auth-service`.`user` ui ON ii.`vendor_id` = ui.`id`
GROUP BY 
    ui.`full_name`
ORDER BY 
    invoice_count DESC
LIMIT 1

170bf2ca4df9014745557d1825ee814f81b48f48.sql:
SELECT 
    ui.`full_name` AS vendor_name
FROM 
    `ems-portal-service`.`invoice_info` ii
JOIN 
    `ems-auth-service`.`user` ui ON ii.`vendor_id` = ui.`id`
JOIN 
    `ems-warehouse-service`.`warehouse_info` wi ON ii.`warehouse_id` = wi.`id`
JOIN 
    `ems-portal-service`.`quick_code_master` qcm ON wi.`city_id` = qcm.`id`
WHERE 
    qcm.`name` = 'Gurgaon'
GROUP BY 
    ui.`full_name` LIMIT 1000

e922c81e63b570b306804cf649ccc09024b893c3.sql:
SELECT 
    ii.`invoice_month`,
    COUNT(ii.`id`) AS invoice_count
FROM 
    `ems-portal-service`.`invoice_info` ii
JOIN 
    `ems-account-service`.`account_info` ai ON ii.`account_id` = ai.`id`
WHERE 
    ai.`account_name` = 'Apollo Tyres'
GROUP BY 
    ii.`invoice_month`
ORDER BY 
    ii.`invoice_month` LIMIT 1000

5a6fdf1b323f85d6998211835850021235f577c6.sql:
SELECT 
    ii.`invoice_month`,
    COUNT(ii.`id`) AS invoice_count
FROM 
    `ems-portal-service`.`invoice_info` ii
JOIN 
    `ems-account-service`.`account_info` ai ON ii.`account_id` = ai.`id`
WHERE 
    ai.`account_name` = 'Apollo Tyres LTD'
GROUP BY 
    ii.`invoice_month`
ORDER BY 
    ii.`invoice_month`  LIMIT 1000

cf3f396140ddefbfb4f2ecd9aea766c1c65f4f7e.sql:
SELECT 
    ii.`invoice_month`,
    COUNT(ii.`id`) AS invoice_count
FROM 
    `ems-portal-service`.`invoice_info` ii
JOIN 
    `ems-account-service`.`account_info` ai ON ii.`account_id` = ai.`id`
WHERE 
    ai.`account_name` = 'Apollo Tyres LTD'
AND ii.`invoice_month` >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 3 MONTH)
GROUP BY 
    ii.`invoice_month`
ORDER BY 
    ii.`invoice_month`  LIMIT 1000

afb5b20f3af08134d4d5af5b1f374bb360cb3005.sql:
SELECT 
    ai.`account_name`
FROM 
    `ems-portal-service`.`invoice_info` ii
JOIN 
    `ems-account-service`.`account_info` ai ON ii.`account_id` = ai.`id`
WHERE 
    ii.`invoice_month` = DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE(), '%Y-%m')
GROUP BY 
    ai.`account_name`
HAVING 
    COUNT(ii.`id`) > (SELECT COUNT(ii2.`id`) FROM `ems-portal-service`.`invoice_info` ii2 JOIN `ems-account-service`.`account_info` ai2 ON ii2.`account_id` = ai2.`id` WHERE ai2.`account_name` = 'Apollo Tyres LTD' AND ii2.`invoice_month` = DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE(), '%Y-%m'))
ORDER BY 
    ai.`account_name` LIMIT 1000

b2f28013601c671d1cff35eeb18a0770fddd44f5.sql:
SELECT 
    qcm.`name` AS region,
    SUM(ii.`total_amount`) AS total_spend
FROM 
    `ems-portal-service`.`invoice_info` ii
JOIN 
    `ems-warehouse-service`.`warehouse_info` wi ON ii.`warehouse_id` = wi.`id`
JOIN 
    `ems-portal-service`.`quick_code_master` qcm ON wi.`zone_id` = qcm.`id`
GROUP BY 
    qcm.`name`  
ORDER BY 
    total_spend DESC LIMIT 1000
